                    "markupType": "Plain",
                    "text": "If the movie star Andrew Garfield weren't promoting his anticipated, big-budget action movie, &#34;The Amazing Spider-Man,&#34; he would be climbing Mount Kilimanjaro.",
                    "value": "",
